# Drop your PLN theme directory here:
#   .obsidian/themes/PLN/theme.css
#   .obsidian/themes/PLN/manifest.json
#
# If the directory is missing, Obsidian falls back to the default theme on
# first open and prompts you to install one. The PLN theme reference lives
# in .obsidian/appearance.json (cssTheme: "PLN").
